{"tid":1448292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:03.000Z","uid":287411,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3927852a47c09d20762b97d0e6b53e532abc1f4d","tid":1448292,"uid":287411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:15.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=b7e9725c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=6cd29f11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"8d0cc60b3f0c57940916a57a6d4a38cb8a4776c8","tid":1448292,"uid":287411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:27.000Z","msg":"push 10 下"},{"pid":"66a4671db3654c2f4b29208c53b9dcc41f206e09","tid":1448292,"uid":287411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:40.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"4959881937b0e75f509349d278cc4779b942248e","tid":1448292,"uid":287411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:51.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"7944f9d7d1a1c1198629783a851e251172a8098a","tid":1448292,"uid":148152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:09.000Z","msg":"標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Po